1
00:00:11,120 --> 00:00:11,800
We're safe.

2
00:00:12,120 --> 00:00:13,120
We're okay for now.

3
00:00:14,720 --> 00:00:15,880
This place...

4
00:00:15,880 --> 00:00:17,360
...is most peculiar.

5
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:19,200
This is my home.

6
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:20,200
Stay here and don't move around.

7
00:00:20,640 --> 00:00:22,320
I'll find some of my dad's clothes for you to change into.

8
00:00:24,040 --> 00:00:26,040
How does one wear this?

9
00:00:27,680 --> 00:00:28,640
Sweetie!

10
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:29,560
She's back.

11
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:32,240
Quick, hide yourself.

12
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:33,040
My mom is back.

13
00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:35,880
It is only right to meet your mother.

14
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:41,880
Mom, I'm here.

15
00:00:42,680 --> 00:00:43,920
You're dressed so nicely.

16
00:00:43,920 --> 00:00:44,920
What are you up to?

17
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:45,920
Your face is so red.

18
00:00:46,360 --> 00:00:47,760
N-Nothing.

19
00:00:47,760 --> 00:00:49,200
I just got back from a comic convention.

20
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,120
Mom, do you need something?

21
00:00:50,600 --> 00:00:51,760
Something's off with you.

22
00:00:52,440 --> 00:00:53,240
You...

23
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:54,360
Are you dating someone?

24
00:00:56,440 --> 00:00:57,280
Mom!

25
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:59,800
It's written all over your face.

26
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:01,160
Stop pretending.

27
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:01,960
Come on, tell me.

28
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:04,000
It's not that I won't say.

29
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:06,640
I'm just afraid you won't believe me.

30
00:01:07,720 --> 00:01:09,760
Your old mom has seen it all.

31
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:12,280
Even if your boyfriend were an alien...

32
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,360
...I could accept it.

33
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:17,840
Well, he's not an alien...

34
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:18,880
...but...

35
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:20,240
...he is an ancient man.

36
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,040
Or rather...

37
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,840
...a man of legend.

38
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,600
Who is it, exactly?

39
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:29,160
Li Jing.

40
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:30,960
Li Jing?

41
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:32,680
Yeah.

42
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:34,960
Which Li Jing?

43
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:36,160
You know...

44
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:37,560
Nezha's dad.

45
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,160
Wow, sweetie.

46
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:42,240
Dating Li Jing, are we?

47
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,440
That's easy to handle.

48
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,440
Get married!

49
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,240
And then...

50
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:46,240
...hurry up and have kids.

51
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:48,840
The first two go to the Bodhisattva, so we won't worry.

52
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,880
Leave Nezha to me and your dad to raise.

53
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:52,240
We won't let him go wreaking havoc in the sea again.

54
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:52,960
Nezha...

55
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:53,600
And then...

56
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:54,840
Alright, alright, Mom.

57
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,840
I know what I'm doing.

58
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:58,280
Wait, I haven't finished explaining!

59
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:09,080
Our mother certainly thinks ahead.

60
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:11,240
She has even chosen the child's name.

61
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,000
The name Nezha...

62
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:15,640
...sounds pleasant.

63
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:16,760
Hey, shut up!

64
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:17,600
Hurry up and change.

65
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,000
Let's go.

66
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,240
I'll take you to buy an outfit.

67
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,320
Oh, don't be shy.

68
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:23,280
Let me have a look.

69
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,520
Holding your hand,

70
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,680
growing old together.

71
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,480
Sir, Miss.

72
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:57,480
You have great taste.

73
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,880
This is our new wedding ring for this season.

74
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,080
May I ask the shopkeeper,

75
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,200
this ring,

76
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,000
costs how many taels of silver?

77
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,160
Sorry about that.

78
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:07,360
Let's go.

79
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,840
Try our famous Tianjin dish.

80
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,200
The mortal world

81
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,720
actually has such delicious food.

82
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:20,880
Eat more of this.

83
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:21,920
Pork kidney.

84
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:25,040
Maybe it can restore your magical power.

85
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:34,600
Do you like it?

86
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:37,960
Then...

87
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,920
Do you like this world?

88
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,760
This world is wonderful.

89
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,960
Peaceful and prosperous.

90
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,840
Peaceful and serene.

91
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:48,840
Compared to Chentang Pass?

92
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,920
If you could choose,

93
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,000
where would you want to live?

94
00:04:01,440 --> 00:04:02,560
If you could choose,

95
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:04,640
where would you want to live?

96
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:05,920
But Chentang Pass needs me.

97
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:12,520
Li Jing.

98
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,880
Then let me send you home.

99
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:25,520
Here,

100
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:26,320
there is a treasure

101
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:27,920
that can send you home.

102
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,160
And you?

103
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,840
It is this treasure.

104
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:33,680
Yes.

105
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,400
It is...

106
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,360
Yin Yuhan.

107
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,600
Why aren't you at work today?

108
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,160
Who is he?

109
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,120
Manager.

110
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,080
This gentleman

111
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,560
is my friend.

112
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,360
Is this a place where you can just bring anyone in?

113
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,280
Take him away immediately.

114
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:44,960
Manager.

115
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:46,760
He can't leave right now.

116
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,000
No, no, no.

117
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,000
It is what you think.

118
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,400
Yin Yuhan.

119
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:54,160
Cultural relics belong to the people!

120
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,760
Don't be foolish!

121
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:58,000
Manager, Manager.

122
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:58,960
Don't misunderstand.

123
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,280
It's not what you think.

124
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:02,040
Explain yourself clearly to me.

125
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,040
This humble one is

126
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,760
Li Jing, Transport Commissioner of Chentang Pass.

127
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:06,880
Greetings,

128
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:08,440
Manager.

129
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,560
Greetings, Senior Jing.

130
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,360
He just time-traveled here.

131
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,560
He's not quite adapted yet.

132
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,360
Time travel?

133
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:17,360
Do you take me for a child?

134
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,560
I can show you.

135
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,360
Come, come, come.

136
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,120
Show me.

137
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:25,440
Yin Yuhan.

138
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,800
How did you graduate?

139
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:29,840
Don't you know blood reacts with copper ions?

140
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:31,240
Oh, what are you waiting for?

141
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,600
Handle it quickly!

142
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,160
What's going on?

143
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,560
Why is there no reaction?

144
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:45,200
The aura here is particularly strong.

145
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,200
Let's split up and look.

146
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:48,560
Right, let's go.
